Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,humility takes a dietary form.\NPorridge and turnups. That's all you get
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Hardly any clothes to wear.\NForget turning on the heat in the winter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,time. Austerity and renunciation.\NAnd then you become a rack of bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said, there's no\Nsuch thing as polarities. What we see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,here is the presence of heat. And as the\Npresence of heat diminishes now we call
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it something different. We call it cold\Nand we call this zero. But you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's arbitrary. There's only one\Nvariable. The presence of heat or its
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,absence. That's all.\NThere's the presence of love or its
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,absence.\Nabsence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So we become friendly. The first form\Nthat forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming benign, benevolent, forgiving,\Ngenerous, compassionate, accepting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,affectionate\Nis toward yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We practice it by looking out into the\Nworld and seeing what is it out there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're still still judgmental about,\Ncan't accept, can't forgive, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's within yourself. Project\Nthat out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world serves then it serves us\Nspiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that the structure of society and its\Noperations are
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego projected out there for us to\Nunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that way the world serves us. It's a\Nconstant source of teaching, of
