Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's out there and it's them\Nbecause of guilt. We don't see it within
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,oursel.\NWe become more sensitive to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what we do is because we're\Nspiritually committed is we let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,within ourself.\NAnd in so doing we serve the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that we let go within ourself\Nwe let go also
