Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,affecting everyone. So\Num let's see if that's so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,\Neverything I serve within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore serves the world. Is this\Neverything you do within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you're thereby serving the world. Why?\NBecause you're part of the world. So you
